      <h1>How Brands Use Video Production to Promote Webinars</h1>
      <p class="lead">See how brands use teaser, countdown, and follow-up videos to drive webinar registrations and turn prospects into engaged leads.</p>
      <p class="post-meta"><span>Sofia Treviño</span> <span>·</span> <span>June 26, 2024</span> <span>·</span> <span>Updated March 25, 2025</span></p>
